                            How do I make new study cards?
                          </span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="display: none;" class="fact">
                        <td class="fact">
                          <p>
                            First, create a new document. You can take notes however you like (paragraphs, outline format, etc). When you come across a term, important date, etc., use a dash to tell StudyEgg to make a card. An example:
                          </p>
                          <p style="padding-left:15px; font-style:italic; color:#666;">
                            Zendo - A Japanese term meaning "meditation hall"
                          </p>
                          <p>
                            This will create a flash card with the term "Zendo" on one side, and the phrase "A Japanese term meaning 'meditation hall'" on the other.
                          </p>
                          <p>
                            For more information, check out the tutorial video:
                          </p>
