                            Why will I become a more efficient learner with StudyEgg?
                          </span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="display: none;" class="fact">
                        <td class="fact">
                          <p>
                            You will become a more efficient learner with StudyEgg in a few ways. First, by using flashcards and answering questions, you are engaging in test-based learning. Research has shown that repeated testing is at the heart of effective learning. StudyEgg also helps you to focus on the information that really matters and study only what you have forgotten. This is accomplished by estimating the importance of your review materials based upon how often you review a card, and how well you knew it (how you graded yourself).
                          </p>
                        </td>
